<div class="welcome-container">
  <div class="p2 bg-white border rounded my2 mx-auto welcome-text">
    <p>StreamFinder is an application geared towards environmental consultants and scientists looking to find water quality monitoring stations throughout Colorado.  The station data is retrieved from the <a href="https://www.waterqualitydata.us/webservices_documentation/" target="_blank">Water Quality Portal Web Service</a> and made available in an easy to navigate map interface.  By adding monitoring stations to a particular project, users can view recent data from the station (streamflow, water quality results, etc.) and search for specific historical data.  Historical data is provided by way of the USGS Water Data Web Service.</p>
  </div>

</div>

